314
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:25,361
to understand

315
00:15:25,361 --> 00:15:26,680
how AI works.

316
00:15:27,121 --> 00:15:28,520
Next, I conducted thorough research

317
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:30,920
on China's regulatory framework,
landmark court rulings,

318
00:15:30,920 --> 00:15:32,601
and extensive international legislation

319
00:15:32,601 --> 00:15:34,201
and judicial literature on AI.

320
00:15:34,481 --> 00:15:36,280
Finally,
I drafted the initial legal opinion.

321
00:15:37,481 --> 00:15:39,601
Then I mainly proposed
the following suggestions.

322
00:15:40,201 --> 00:15:40,880
First,

323
00:15:41,081 --> 00:15:43,321
