327
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:49,560
Yiaiwan does not
claim ownership of these.

328
00:15:49,920 --> 00:15:50,640
Second...

329
00:15:50,640 --> 00:15:53,040
Hold on. The rest
of your opinion is good.

330
00:15:53,400 --> 00:15:55,560
About the first point,
what is your rationale?

331
00:15:56,001 --> 00:15:58,121
Why advise Yiaiwan to waive its rights?

332
00:15:59,040 --> 00:16:01,361
Mr. Song, indeed, I advise Yiaiwan

333
00:16:01,361 --> 00:16:03,601
not to assert rights
over user-generated content.

334
00:16:03,800 --> 00:16:05,321
This seems not to benefit our client,

335
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:07,721
but after thorough market research,

336
00:16:07,721 --> 00:16:08,961
I reached this conclusion.

337
00:16:09,201 --> 00:16:09,800
I believe

338
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:11,640
that if Yiaiwan offers this concession,

339
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:13,081
after launching their model,

340
00:16:13,081 --> 00:16:13,760
it will create

341
00:16:13,841 --> 00:16:15,280
a strong user acquisition advantage.

342
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:16,560
Commercially speaking,

343
00:16:16,760 --> 00:16:17,961
this benefits Yiaiwan.

344
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:20,121
This is a business decision,

345
00:16:20,441 --> 00:16:22,760
so I explicitly stated
in the legal opinion

346
00:16:23,001 --> 00:16:24,001
that Yiaiwan must

347
00:16:24,001 --> 00:16:25,560
carefully weigh this

348
00:16:25,721 --> 00:16:26,560
against their goals.

349
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:29,280
Honestly,

350
00:16:30,040 --> 00:16:31,241
on this matter,

351
00:16:31,361 --> 00:16:32,961
our thinking aligns perfectly.

352
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:36,481
Besides, you included
supporting materials. I'm impressed.

353
00:16:37,601 --> 00:16:38,361
Really?

354
00:16:39,160 --> 00:16:39,880
Thank you.

355
00:16:40,121 --> 00:16:41,160
How time flies.

356
00:16:41,880 --> 00:16:42,800
Remember when you

357
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:44,400
used to cry and demand to leave?

358
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:45,760
You are more capable now.

359
00:16:46,201 --> 00:16:47,081
I was concerned

360
00:16:47,481 --> 00:16:50,481
