might affect your work for Yiaiwan.

361
00:16:51,361 --> 00:16:53,121
But aren't you the one who taught us

362
00:16:53,481 --> 00:16:55,361
to leverage every possible advantage?

363
00:16:56,241 --> 00:16:57,081
As the ex-girlfriend

364
00:16:57,241 --> 00:16:59,520
