and must be exhausted.

538
00:25:46,560 --> 00:25:47,760
You couldn't come, right?

539
00:25:49,120 --> 00:25:50,401
I'm fine, not too tired.

540
00:25:50,560 --> 00:25:51,840
I slept during the flight.

541
00:25:57,600 --> 00:25:59,880
Xiaoyu, my phone's out of power.
I'll call back later.

542
00:26:08,441 --> 00:26:08,961
What's wrong?

543
00:26:10,001 --> 00:26:12,001
I sent you so many messages,
