544
00:26:14,921 --> 00:26:15,481
Out of power.

545
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:17,641
How could you block me then?

546
00:26:18,441 --> 00:26:19,600
I saw you speaking on a call.

547
00:26:20,280 --> 00:26:23,320
Did I do something wrong?
Are you mad at me?

548
00:26:25,280 --> 00:26:27,241
If you need to reach me, call me

549
00:26:27,840 --> 00:26:29,241
or use office software.

550
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:30,641
Between colleagues,

551
00:26:30,921 --> 00:26:31,800
that's sufficient.

552
00:26:51,161 --> 00:26:52,296
Why are you following me?

553
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:54,721
You didn't respond
to my WeChat messages.

554
00:26:56,001 --> 00:26:57,161
I asked when you'd arrive,

555
00:26:57,161 --> 00:26:58,120
and you blocked me.

556
00:26:58,120 --> 00:27:00,161
I reread our chat history so many times,

557
00:27:00,161 --> 00:27:01,760
but still couldn't find the problem.

558
00:27:01,760 --> 00:27:03,840
I tried hard to get close to Mr. Zhou

559
00:27:03,840 --> 00:27:04,520
just to find out

560
00:27:04,520 --> 00:27:06,001
when your flight actually landed.

561
00:27:07,040 --> 00:27:10,080
I didn't pick you up at the airport
as I worried they might misunderstand.

562
00:27:10,681 --> 00:27:12,441
So I waited outside your home instead.

563
00:27:12,441 --> 00:27:13,320
But then you just said

564
00:27:14,961 --> 00:27:16,201
